		<Question><TranslatedText>Eligibility Questions   The following questions will help us to determine whether you are eligible for the study.</TranslatedText><redcap:FormattedTranslatedText>&lt;div class=&quot;rich-text-field-label&quot;&gt;&lt;h6 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Eligibility Questions&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt; &lt;h6&gt;The following questions will help us to determine whether you are eligible for the study.&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</redcap:FormattedTranslatedText></Question>
	</ItemDef>
